1. What are the advantages of using slice of strings?
->Slices of string in python is a more powerful option to handel string than the array approach it not only minimize code but make it more user friendly.

2. Can you directly replace a character in string just by assigning? If not,state the reason. Also give the solution.
->We can replace substring in string not character.If we have to do we have to use a character as a substring.

3. What is the use of negative index?
->Negetive index is used in certain functions in python to get position from the end of string in some special cases it is used.
